y became criminal/sinful (subject of كَانُوا)","transliteration":"ajramū","root":"جرم","lemmaId":1216},{"id":"83:29:4","ayahNum":29,"wordNum":4,"word":"كَانُوا۟","meaning":"they were","transliteration":"kānū","root":"كون","lemmaId":null},{"id":"83:29:5","ayahNum":29,"wordNum":5,"word":"مِنَ","meaning":"from (connects to ٱلَّذِينَ)","transliteration":"mina","root":"","lemmaId":3464},{"id":"83:29:6","ayahNum":29,"wordNum":6,"word":"الذين","meaning":"those who","transliteration":"alladhīna","root":"","lemmaId":null},{"id":"83:29:7","ayahNum":29,"wordNum":7,"word":"ءَامَنُوا۟","meaning":"they believed (subject of يَضْحَكُونَ - they laugh)","transliteration":"āmanū","root":"أمن","lemmaId":334},{"id":"83:29:8","ayahNum":29,"wordNum":8,"word":"يَضْحَكُونَ","meaning":"they laugh","transliteration":"yaḍḥakūna","root":"ضحك","lemmaId":null},{"id":"83:30:1","ayahNum":30,"wordNum":1,"word":"وَإِذَا","meaning":"and when (connecting to what happened before)","transliteration":"wa-idhā","root":"","lemmaId":4646},{"id":"83:30:2","ayahNum":30,"wordNum":2,"word":"مَرُّوا۟","meaning":"they passed by","transliteration":"marrū","root":"مرر","lemmaId":null},{"id":"83:30:3","ayahNum":30,"wordNum":3,"word":"بِهِمْ","meaning":"by/with them (object of يَتَغَامَزُونَ)","transliteration":"bihim","root":"","lemmaId":692},{"id":"83:30:4","ayahNum":30,"wordNum":4,"word":"يَتَغَامَزُونَ","meaning":"they wink at each other","transliteration":"yataghāmazūna","root":"غمز","lemmaId":null},{"id":"83:31:1","ayahNum":31,"wordNum":1,"word":"وَإِذَا","meaning":"and when (connects to what happened before)","transliteration":"wa-idhā","root":"","lemmaId":4646},{"id":"83:31:2","ayahNum":31,"wordNum":2,"word":"اِنْقَلَبُوا","meaning":"they turned themselves/returned (to أَهْلِهِمُ their families)","transliteration":"inqalabū","root":"قلب","lemmaId":2972},{"id":"83:31:3","ayahNum":31,"wordNum":3,"word":"إِلَىٰٓ","meaning":"to/towards (connecting to أَهْلِهِمُ)","transliteration":"ilā","root":"","lemmaId":485},{"